he difference of the </div><div class="t m9b8 x26 h28 y780 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">offerings. This line of argument he continues un-</div><div class="t m3c7 x26 h28 y79a ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">til he conies to the close of all priestly work, and </div><div class="t m7a0 x26 h28 y56e ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the coming agaifi of the Son of God unto the full </div><div class="t m9b9 x26 h28 y8d8 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">salvation of them that look for him. </div><div class="t m9ba x10 h50 y6d4 ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON N.V. </div><div class="t m85d x69 h25 y8d9 ff4 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">JANUARY II, </div><div class="t m9bb x1b h2b y8d9 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I890. </div><div class="t m9bc x30 h33 y73 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">HEBREWS 8: 2-6. </div><div class="t m9bd x28 h2b y810 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. IN </div><div class="t mda x12 h28 y810 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Mosaic dispensation, did God have a </div><div class="t m90 x18 h28 y55f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">dwelling-place among his people ? </div><div class="t m136 x28 h28 y6d9 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m13c x5b h28 y6d9 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Where was it made? and by whom? </div><div class="t m139 x28 h28 y8da ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m9be x5b h28 y8da ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What were its two rooms called? </div><div class="t m13e x28 h28 y883 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m464 x5b h28 y8db ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Who were permitted to go into the sanctuary? </div><div class="t m7cb x4a h28 y628 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Num. 18:1-7. </div><div class="t m142 x28 h28 y8dc ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t ma5 x5b h28 y8dd ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How often did the priests go into the holy </div><div class="t m3b2 x4a h28 y8de ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">place ? Heb. 9: 6. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
